Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.02,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.86,0:00:18.95,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,The purported Entrances, tears in reality that\Nconnected the human realm to another dimension,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.46,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,suddenly appeared all over the planet.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.96,0:00:27.09,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,Every military force on the planet\Nsuffered a horrible defeat,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.09,0:00:31.46,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,never truly knowing who they were fighting.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.98,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,The Entrances vanished two\Nweeks after they appeared,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.89,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,and the danger seemed to have passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.10,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.36,0:00:49.11,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,...they returned.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.15,0:00:56.78,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,The world's governments\Nevacuated to oceanic Megafloats.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.78,0:01:01.49,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,However, only a small portion of\Nthe population was able to escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.58,0:01:09.00,Default,R,0,0,0,,The world is still being invaded by enemies\Npouring in from the open Entrances.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.71,0:01:16.30,Default,R,0,0,0,,But we haven't been sitting\Nhere twiddling our thumbs.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.30,0:01:21.39,Default,R,0,0,0,,We've developed the Heart Hybrid Gears,\Nwhich let us face the enemy on equal ground.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.70,Default,R,0,0,0,,This is Ataraxia's Heart Hybrid\NGear ace team, Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.40,Default,R,0,0,0,,They're some of our most important fighters.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.65,Default,R,0,0,0,,Great work today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.82,Default,R,0,0,0,,As principal and high commander\Nof Ataraxia, I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sis, are you seriously the principal\N{\i1}and{\i0} high commander?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.91,0:01:42.79,Default,R,0,0,0,,And now we have the means\Nto make Gears even stronger.
