Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.33,0:01:49.79,Default,R,0,0,0,,This is Hida Kizuna, a 2nd-year student\Njoining the High School Tactical Division.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.38,Default,R,0,0,0,,It's already been decided that he'll join\NAmaterasu upon enrolling at the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.80,Default,R,0,0,0,,This is the key to our victory.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.72,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Wow!
