Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, figures...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.41,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kizuna.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.41,Default,Y,0,0,0,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.00,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Hey, perv!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.54,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Julicia Farandole{-sama} is an American\Nmilitary ace {\i1}and{\i0} a rich celebrity!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.92,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,You're not even worthy of speaking to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.17,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Now, now. Calm down, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.76,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hey, is what the high commander said true?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.76,0:07:37.06,Default,Y,0,0,0,,If I seek pleasure with you,\Nwill my Hybrid Count really go back up?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,I-I don't really know...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Farandole{-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.73,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Call me Julicia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.73,0:07:47.07,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Would you like to try right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.82,Default,H,0,0,0,,Julicia{-san}, a classroom is a sacred place,\Nso I won't let you do anything indecent here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.57,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Then it's fine as long as we're not in the classroom?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.79,Default,H,0,0,0,,No, it's not fine anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.87,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.21,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.96,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Sylvia Silkcut, Middle School Year 1!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.80,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,The commander wants to\Ntalk to you, Captain Kizuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.09,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,This is the Heart Hybrid Gear research lab,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.35,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,also known as the Nayuta Labs.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.81,0:08:21.10,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,The basic technology behind the\NHybrid Gears was developed here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's Dr. Hida Nayuta, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.23,Default,K,0,0,0,,The super-important person\Nwho developed the Gears.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.65,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sylvia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.28,Default,R,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.04,Default,R,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.04,Default,R,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.21,Default,R,0,0,0,,This is the lab's director,\NChief Engineer Shikina Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.80,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.51,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,I am Shikina Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.80,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,You can call me Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.31,Default,R,0,0,0,,Well, don't let it bug you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.06,Default,R,0,0,0,,Anyway, Kizuna, I'll give you this to start with.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.27,Default,R,0,0,0,,It's a portable terminal that also\Nfunctions as a student handbook.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.15,Default,R,0,0,0,,Yours is special.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.36,Default,R,0,0,0,,Tap the icons of the Amaterasu members.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,This is private information!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.49,Default,R,0,0,0,,That's why it's special.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.58,Default,R,0,0,0,,You can see one of the listings\Nis for Hybrid Count, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.62,0:09:26.79,Default,R,0,0,0,,When their count goes below five percent,\Nit becomes difficult to maintain their Gears.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.46,Default,R,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.63,Default,K,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.63,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.21,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,If you Hybrid Heart, the count will recover.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Gear energy doesn't recover naturally?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.14,Default,R,0,0,0,,Natural recovery takes far too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.35,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,And the energy loss in combat is huge.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.72,0:09:47.85,Default,R,0,0,0,,So we need you and your Gear, Eros.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.36,Default,R,0,0,0,,Our latest research shows\Nthat Eros has a special function.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.36,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Heart Hybrid, a technique that\Ncan rapidly restore Hybrid Counts.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.49,Default,R,0,0,0,,It's no exaggeration to say that the fate\Nof humanity rests on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.87,Default,R,0,0,0,,Do your job as captain justice.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.63,Default,R,0,0,0,,Starting today, you're the captain of Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,But that's so sudden!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.26,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll help as best I can!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.34,Default,R,0,0,0,,Sylvia is going to keep me updated\Non whether things are proceeding smoothly
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.34,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,between you and the members of Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.01,0:10:22.76,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.26,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,This is crazy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.52,Default,R,0,0,0,,Work hard. You've got a mission now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,A mission?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.02,0:10:30.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.98,Default,R,0,0,0,,I'll go over the mission details again.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.40,0:10:39.99,Default,R,0,0,0,,Your job is to gather data on a nearby\Nisland and recover resource samples.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.78,Default,R,0,0,0,,This is your first mission as Amaterasu's captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.74,Default,R,0,0,0,,Stay sharp out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,How can someone so indecent be our captain?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.70,0:10:50.25,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'll go on ahead and scope out the area!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait a second—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.79,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayuru, you're so silly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.67,Default,R,0,0,0,,Julicia.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.01,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Oh? What is it, High Commander?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.47,Default,R,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.47,0:11:03.85,Default,R,0,0,0,,Your Hybrid Count is at twenty percent.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.64,Default,R,0,0,0,,Avoid combat as much as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.98,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This place is safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.65,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you worry about\Nyour little brother instead?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.40,Default,Y,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't seem like he's flying very steadily...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.82,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go catch up to Hayuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,They're both so fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.08,0:11:30.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,Hayuru is Japan's ace,\Nand Julicia is America's.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,By the way, how good are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,Japan's #2?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,Or some foreign ace?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.38,Default,A,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.30,Default,A,0,0,0,,I'm the ace of the entire Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,Earth?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,Oh no, I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.81,Default,A,0,0,0,,I meant the entire universe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,The entire universe, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.82,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Data recovery initiated.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.07,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,It will take two hours or so to finish.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,So we get our samples during that time?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.91,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go, Kizuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.08,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Make sure you escort me right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.96,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.13,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You're such a worrywart, aren't you, Kizuna?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.64,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Entrances only appear on land\Nmasses above a certain size.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.39,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That means this tiny island is safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.48,Default,Y,0,0,0,,So, what are the specs on your Gear?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,Not exactly sure how to answer that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.98,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.73,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What's your kill score, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,Zero.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.53,Default,Y,0,0,0,,So what, you're really a complete rookie?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.74,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Any combat experience?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,The battle yesterday was my first.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.37,0:12:53.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,Though all I did was grab Chidorigafuchi as she fell.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything else, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,How many enemies have you defeated, Julicia?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.09,Default,Y,0,0,0,,About three hundred.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,Three—?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's America's ace for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.26,Default,Y,0,0,0,,There's nothing amazing about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,Julicia?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.27,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Come, let's regroup with Hayuru and Aine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.82,Default,H,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.78,Default,H,0,0,0,,Aine{-san}, let's go meet Julicia{-san} and—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.49,Default,H,0,0,0,,An Entrance?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.95,Default,H,0,0,0,,No, that doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,Equip your Gear, Hayuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.34,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,This is Kizuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,Ataraxia, come in!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shikina{-san}! Sis!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.18,0:14:39.90,Default,Y,0,0,0,,When an Entrance appears,\Nnormal communications stop working.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.06,Default,Y,0,0,0,,But Gear users can talk to one another.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.61,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Aine? Hayuru?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.86,Default,Y,0,0,0,,No... why?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,Julicia{-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.12,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hida{-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.83,0:14:54.79,Default,H,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.33,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hayuru, look!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.87,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.38,Default,H,0,0,0,,Blade!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.59,Default,H,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.39,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\t(1370,0,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}We're locked in?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.64,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Kizuna, go grab the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,But then you'll be all by yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.27,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You'll just slow me down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.40,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.65,Default,K,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Eros!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.07,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.16,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You boys ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,A girl's risking her life in combat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,Julicia!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.51,Default,Y,0,0,0,,My Hybrid Count is down to six percent.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.76,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That's cutting it awfully close.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.70,Default,Y,0,0,0,,A Dragorie?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.03,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That's a Category-A Magitech weapon.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.16,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.46,Default,Y,0,0,0,,My beam's power is dropping!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.59,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I can't move my hands...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Or my legs...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.63,Default,Y,0,0,0,,My body feels so heavy...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.94,Default,Y,0,0,0,,My chest...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Julicia!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Kizuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.88,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.47,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.14,Default,k,0,0,0,,Julicia...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Run...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.39,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.56,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this for me\Nwhen we've only just met?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.90,0:17:33.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,A girl's... in danger...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,Of course I have to help her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.66,Default,Y,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the only reason he did this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,Run, Julicia!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.84,Default,Y,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.22,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Kizuna...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.97,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.61,Default,Y,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.67,Default,Y,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this sensation?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.63,0:18:40.43,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Amazing. My whole body\Nis overflowing with power!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.64,0:18:45.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,So this is a Heart Hybrid?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.23,0:18:55.32,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to save me, Kizuna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.95,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.41,0:19:06.45,Default,Y,0,0,0,,This is my...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.21,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Showtime!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.38,0:19:15.21,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hellfire!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.36,Default,A,0,0,0,,This time!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.53,Default,A,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.45,Default,H,0,0,0,,The Entrance is gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.37,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Aine! Hayuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.37,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.66,Default,H,0,0,0,,Julicia{-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.08,Default,H,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.62,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Best I've ever been!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.62,0:19:54.58,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I did a Heart Hybrid with Kizuna,\Nand now I'm better than ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey, Julicia...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.75,0:20:00.22,Default,H,0,0,0,,So that means you too, Julicia{-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,How could this be?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.77,Default,R,0,0,0,,We let our guard down today.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.69,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,That island increases in size as the tide goes out,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so it became large enough\Nfor an Entrance to appear.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.40,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,We missed that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.73,0:20:22.40,Default,R,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have made Julicia go with\Nsuch a low Hybrid Count if I had known.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.07,0:20:28.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,After her Count got in the red zone,\Nshe seemed to be in a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.92,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to tell him, Reiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.68,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,I think we can wait until you're ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.98,Default,A,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,How could you keep me waiting?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.36,Default,A,0,0,0,,To do a Heart Hybrid, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.03,Default,A,0,0,0,,You don't even understand that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,I refuse to understand!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.07,0:21:04.95,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Kizuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,Julicia?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.95,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Are your wounds okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,What about you? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.50,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.21,Default,Y,0,0,0,,All thanks to you, Kizuna.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.33,Default,Y,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do some more, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm first, Julicia!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.46,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Oh my, Aine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.17,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You want to do a Heart Hybrid again?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.59,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.30,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The one before was basically an accident!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.31,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hida{-kun}, this is Himekawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.31,0:21:33.10,Default,H,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.85,Default,H,0,0,0,,As a fellow Amaterasu member...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.02,Default,H,0,0,0,,How indecent!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.07,Default,H,0,0,0,,Neros!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.69,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'll punish you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.24,Default,A,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.57,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,No fighting in my room!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.12,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,High Commander, I've got my report!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.96,0:21:54.96,ED,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:17.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}How about an apple, Snow White? Relax, it's safe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:22.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}You know, that shit-eating grin really pisses me off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}I'm gonna punch you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:30.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Forgive me for being cold to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}It's just that there was this girl looking at you in the cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}I'm gonna kill her
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}She'd probably leave you before the night is over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:45.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H44198C&}Let me show you the storm of emotions trapped beneath the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:52.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H44198C&}Go beyond your dreams, love's waiting for you there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:57.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFB3CE7&}What do you want so badly that you'd cry for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:03.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFC833E&}All I want is your heart's warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:08.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H5A57FF&}There's no escape from the love that's seeping through your veins
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:11.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HDAB29E&}Hold me, hold your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:16.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HDAB29E&}You're my prince
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HDAB29E&}Just kidding
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.96,0:23:25.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Preview}
