Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:32.80,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Megafloat Japan's the perfect place\Nfor a date, isn't it, Kizuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.18,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,{\an8}A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.72,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are Julicia{-san} and Hida{-kun}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.85,Default,Gi,0,0,0,,{\an8}How indecent!
